OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cafter increased demand for emergency
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FThe public is being urged to collect
OL,8,Ftheir relatives from St Mary's
OL,9,FHospital on the Isle of Wight as soon
OL,10,Fas they are ready to be discharged.
OL,12,FThe NHS Trust declared a critical
OL,13,Fincident yesterday (Monday 11 March)
OL,14,Facross its acute and ambulance
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FIt says it's under significant
OL,18,Fpressure with demand for emergency and
OL,19,Furgent care currently outstripping the
OL,20,Fnumber of beds available.
