OL,7,FVictoria Lauchlan, Interim Chief
OL,8,FOperating Officer, from the Trust
OL,9,Fsays: "We currently have a high number
OL,10,Fof people in hospital beds who are
OL,11,Fwaiting for onward care arrangements
OL,12,Fin the community.
OL,14,F"We are working as an island
OL,15,Fhealthcare system to do everything we
OL,16,Fcan to ensure we can help better
OL,17,Fsupport these people to be discharged
OL,18,Fhome with a package of care or to Care
OL,19,Fand Nursing Homes.
