OL,7,F"At this time we are asking people to
OL,8,Fhelp by collecting their relatives or
OL,9,Ffriends as soon as they are ready to
OL,10,Fleave and helping with any additional
OL,11,Fcare and support at home."
OL,13,FJuliet Pearce, Director of Nursing,
OL,14,FMidwifery and AHPs added: "To protect
OL,15,Fthe life-saving services we provide we
OL,16,Fare asking for everyone's support
OL,17,Fincluding using your local healthcare
OL,18,Fservices appropriately."
